author: Patrick Cc:
description:
Brendan Fraser was one of Hollywood’s most promising upcoming Actors.. until he suddenly vanished from the spotlight. Behind his disappearance was a powerful network that punished him for speaking out against the wrong person. This is the story of how the Hollywood elite protected their own, and how Brendan Fraser became the target of an industry that operates more like a mafia than a non-profit.
